snippet.textDisplay: pls.pls. pls. I request my friends over here not to start any hind pak debate here, you know Punjab as one is unbeatable to any world power. Our both punjab's still miss each other, when it was one the greatness of the rich culture the lyrics, the music, the dances, the language, clothes and beautiful people, their rituals, bravery everything is unmatched. So here is a message for everyone in this song for all the world, to every person of whatever nation he/she is ,that how one should love its country and countrymen and pay respect to its national flag. so my dear Punjabi's  of both punjab's pls see your roots and then you won't fight, you will love each other, as Punjabi's always did to everyone.
